                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-11-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">接受挑战，倾听内心的神高之声</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="26744208">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-26744208" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-26744208" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="26744208">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
